      "title": "A revised and interim budget in August",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Cabinet Spokesman, Minister of Transport, Highways and Mass Media, Dr. Bandula Gunawardena said today (26th) at the press conference announcing the Cabinet decision held at the Information Department that a revised and interim budget for the next few months will be submitted to the Parliament in August."
